
                                               *minimum-mouse-cursor-height*


    VARIABLE
    *minimum-mouse-cursor-height*  -  lower bound on the height of a mouse
      cursor

    DESCRIPTION
    Bound to a number which is the minimum height for mouse-cursor  bitmaps.
    (Mouse cursors are defined with bitmaps.)

    EXAMPLES
    ;;  This value may be different in your version.
    *minimum-mouse-cursor-height* => 0

    SEE ALSO
    make-mouse-cursor, *maximum-mouse-cursor-height*, *maximum-mouse-
    cursor-width*, *minimum-mouse-cursor-width*















































